{"type": "article", "id": 58261, "title": "Jean Paul Gaultier 想停止使用皮草，以及，米歇尔·奥巴马登《Elle》封面 ｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2018-11-13T10:36:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2968, "name": "Mulberry"}, {"id": 3017, "name": "Jean Paul Gaultier"}, {"id": 15558, "name": "Vince"}, {"id": 25622, "name": "山东如意"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181113181927JoBQx3DFLNKHPUdM.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Jean-Paul-Gaultier-says-no-to-fur,1034275.html#.W-qfwHozZp8\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jean-Paul Gaultier 也在考虑停止使用皮草</a></strong>｜这位法国设计师在法国电视节目 <em>Bonsoir! </em>中表示，他虽然喜欢使用天然皮草，但动物被杀害的方式很悲惨，未来需要考虑放弃使用皮草。这一发言受到了动物权利组织 PETA 的欢迎，该组织全球项目总监 Mimi Bekhechi 表示这一决定“是时代的象征”。但国际毛皮联合会 CEO Mark Oaten 则表示，Jean Paul Gautier 不应该突然听信 PETA 的游说，应该坚持使用天然皮草这种对环境有益的天然可持续材料。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/China-s-Ruyi-owner-of-SMCP-still-on-the-lookout-for-acquisitions-says-chairman,1034512.html#.W-qc23ozZp8\" rel=\"nofollow\">山东如意集团还在寻求收购标的</a></strong>｜该集团主席邱亚夫在《纽约时报》主办的香港国际奢侈品论坛上表示，他不希望集团的对外形象只与收购相关，但遇到合适的品牌还是有收购打算。他同时表示，时尚行业所习惯的季节因素对消费者来说将变得越来越不重要，共享经济和定制化将在奢侈品行业中扮演重要作用。</p><p>如意集团到目前为止收购的品牌和公司包括 Cerruti 1881、Aquascutum 、Gieves &amp; Hawkes、SMCP 集团以及 Bally。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/sportswear/vince-to-launch-unfold-an-online-subscription-service-1202904267/\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国高端时尚品牌 Vince 推出在线订阅服务 Vince Unfold</a></strong>｜通过该服务，消费者每月支付 160 美元后可无限制地选择服饰试穿，并可以 4 折到 8 折的折扣优惠进行购买，并且享受免费优先发货和免费洗衣服务等。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Mulberry-looks-east-for-growth-expects-revenue-pick-up-in-2019,1034471.html#.W-qc3XozZp8\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mulberry 上半年销售额下滑 8%，计划将重心转移至亚洲市场</a></strong>｜&nbsp;Thierry Andretta 在《纽约时报》主办的香港国际奢侈品论坛上表示，明年韩国将成为 Mulberry 仅次于英国的第二大市场，该市场门店数量已经达到 19 个。他同时表示，Mulberry 将尽量减少对于英国市场的依赖，将其占总营收比例从目前的 68% 降至 50%，以减缓退欧造成的影响。他认为亚洲是能够推动增长的重要市场，计划在香港、中国大陆和日本继续扩张，在中国已经与京东旗下奢侈品电商 Toplife、寺库和唯品会签订了合作协议。线上销售占比已从 4 年前的 9% 增至 17%。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/372592/moma-jiangzaicifashou-kawsbff-lansejiheisebanbengongzi/\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约当代艺术博物馆（MoMA）再次发售去年与 KAWS 合作的黑色及蓝色 BFF 搪胶公仔</a></strong>。<br></p><p>于美国东部时间 11 月 14 日上午 10 点起通过 MoMA&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://store.moma.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">线上商店</a>开售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113165605b89oe4E65vBqX1GC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.798148\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/dior-meatpacking-district-holiday-pop-up-store-new-york-1202905190/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dior 在纽约曼哈顿西部的肉库区（Meatpacking District）开出了一家快闪店</a>。</strong><br></p><p>快闪店将持续四个月，并且分成了不同主题风格的房间，不断上架应季产品。Dior 还计划于 11 月 28 日在美国市场正式开通线上旗舰店，并出售由男装创意总监 Kim Jones 设计的胶囊系列。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113170303BUuWMSlXKLJgzhnr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.489019\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113170303VLIoazGTq6PcxpBr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.342606\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113170302fbwy9RiS6vFoPIOQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.685547\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113170305Idl87ZQTmWB1HMOJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131702590UA8E2yrg7JqSLdx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.700195\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113170307dcxtRkTzQaurUKjf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.708008\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113170306f0XzI14MSL2FoJKC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.637695\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113170307Pb7gLp6WsIeQfqHz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.437775\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113170308NZDr3Xl2mFBWgGKP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.682617\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113170308koOhfliHbBS7GKtY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>因与 Adidas Originals 推出合作系列受到瞩目的 <strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/danielle-cathari-launches-namesake-brand-1202903886/\" rel=\"nofollow\">24 岁荷兰设计师&nbsp;Danielle Cathari 推出同名品牌</a></strong>。<br></p><p>在强调街头服饰元素的同时保留了极简的审美趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171104UGHJKdih3XCqA7Qm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171108ajCuBN9IFGK5gAiY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171106QOwcSmWERzDh4gy3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171106YBDT9jzopN2KkM4P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171107bn6hH9vpL43FSEXs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171108RxKPmNQu8F0sa6Di.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171109l1nusixTRqowQNmL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171133zH42NgVn9rDUB8Is.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/372289/m-y-o-b-nyc-fabu-2019-chunxia-lookbook/\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本女装品牌 M.Y.O.B NYC 发布 2019 春夏 Lookbook。</a></strong><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171651DmUHWiNYVIKtf8k6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171646nDrtjSKmbilPv51R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171650CeOiplDxZPBThtK6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131716494rQWDzvVj6n0M7xK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171649G1BZONqDwaUSkF7t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171652Fc6EeOIUBgdaimsN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171659MrozAmLK80Xyqf2b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171653TwseyIDz17Y6AM05.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171654dbEF8SunwOoXr6AB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171654qY60xOMAFErhyfRi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171655W89DLXqaSZsTyf7m.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171656IhDEP8T7mv4rXZiC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131716572ty1UskJhMi4VwOp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171656mGez04rBTcfSuwI6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171659khBGMdyVj647Asev.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171700RKnI3kzlfgJxo5sm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171701f0UhxYM76OgVbW1C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171702gDWm6nLPfopFXYh8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171706P85N3LQnHFxgU2i9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171704hQIYd1u4XBrtL60s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131717074qNtJ2TfLUvXgKih.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171705OESscuhp7BtwDvyG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171708zVNTgbkpu4lcn1CO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171707nXSilqQCbhFJwyxG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171711EXKhjqgsiyldr6bT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171710rX97JjYaGqI6lBgF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171714mh19O6qP2uLHoJgB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113171713L8GmoW19CTg6w57v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.anothermag.com/fashion-beauty/11302/how-to-make-it-as-a-young-creative-according-to-artist-ana-kras\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约摄影师&nbsp;Ana Kraš 为丹麦女装品牌 Ganni 拍摄的 2019 春夏系列大片</a></strong>。<br></p><p>模特为&nbsp;Emma Rosenzweig，也是丹麦的一位艺术家，近期与 Ganni 合作拍摄了一部短片&nbsp;<em>Yesterday, Today &amp; Tomorrow。</em></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162704tpQSe47XYjhbTOa2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.493506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162652fLFZhp7OrGKvymCw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.480456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162654WxuIcA2HO0ozgn4L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.287387\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162655gVvubP2qoeUxZMW7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.493506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162710M2no7KgRADYByeW8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.493506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162704xoNIekLgAXFR6lhz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.493506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162657b2e4hycXU9nzwPYO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.493506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162703u9jLilN6tVpEB4Qw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.480456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162706TKzcDSLrx0v35Bst.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.493506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162707tFNEZRMryTwCqQzV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162708H2JILXCg64rS3ZTE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.493506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162707yYaBzm2q1e3wiNd5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162709aS63GfZL4DFAt7yT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.493506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162710RShAQYnPHumzbr3v.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.480456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113162654m6QAKjaoMrUkeF8O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.669531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131627113XcrmpZ6KCslodUS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.669531\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131627114je1t03gnBbEKJC5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.736190\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2018/11/michelle-obama-elle-magazine-oprah-interview-december-2018\" rel=\"nofollow\">Michelle Obama 登上了美国版《Elle》12 月封面，并且接受了 Oprah Winfrey 的采访</a></strong>。</p><p>采访全文<a href=\"https://www.elle.com/culture/career-politics/a24788222/michelle-obama-november-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">在此</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131731519zpgwusmbj5VXqlr.png\" data-ratio=\"1.255578\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.metmuseum.org/exhibitions/listings/2018/jewelry\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约大都会艺术博物馆（The Met）的新展“Jewelry: The Body Transformed\"</a>。</strong></p><p>展览由 6 位策展人共同策展，探索珠宝的本质及其传递的信息，共包括从公元前 2600 年至今的 230 件展品。较为特别的是，展览严格按照时间线而非不同文明划分展区，将珠宝视为能够反映相应时代的微缩雕塑，而非单纯是一件对外展示个人风格的配饰。展期从 2018 年 11 月 12 日持续至 2019 年 2 月 24 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164651eou2OivjFrUYnQmb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.535000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164646ZkCF3KtXWNQ0A9d7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.577000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164650g1ue8bD4t3xzQn7c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.914077\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164649gYa2tHuOc1UAqNfm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.022000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131646506wXVE0WeUIkmhsjJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.763359\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164648ENxvZrenyO6mjFsQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.845547\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131646527cV3XqK9tf2DeOlg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164653QypajmScvs5ub1Lh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.726500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164657BXpyP2IEsabVNSFZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.681000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131646592TYEZ1o9nlw85HLO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.706500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164658V54nzoqPkNdfZMuO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.730500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164656YNs9nStq4JklOyvF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.996016\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131646481e9aBk8uEtlYRnVL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.050000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164653MfwtrxSqjciHW62l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.249333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164647vFBi1AHlKXD4GV7T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.198667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164656eLGFDtzsy0IwjPpr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.116625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131646498hEoj6R1HZzUtJ2X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.182667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164654FrohEf37U5lRwayi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.298000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164655J36HbprI9DoABsPC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334223\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164652sjEWiVbU5ofcQr9t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164700F4HrtgvicLQbO7kz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.134430\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181113164659tHKDOsdafbV0hWcy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.303781\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811131646510IGieW8yVwHlAp4b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.749500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p0792oia4ih\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p>题图为<a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/film-tv/article/42170/1/luca-guadagnino-suspiria-call-me-by-your-name-interview\" rel=\"nofollow\">&nbsp;Dakota Johnson in <em>Suspiria</em></a><br></p>"}